  "name": "Powerful Connection",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/items/inventory/book-purple.jpg",
  "sort": 0,
  "flags": {},
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When casting a divination spell (such as scrying) that imposes a penalty on saving throws based on the physical connection you have to the target, you can expend 1 point of mental focus to double the penalty from a possession, garment, or body part.</p>\n<p>In addition, when casting any other divination spell that allows a saving throw, you can increase the DC of that save by 2 by adding an object, garment, or body part that belonged to the target as a focus component for the spell and expending 1 point of mental focus.</p>"
